title: Antonio Conte despairs after Chelsea drop points at Burnley and says SIX teams are in the hunt for the Premier League title
text:
EFL BLUE IT Antonio Conte despairs after Chelsea drop points at Burnley and says SIX teams are in the hunt for the Premier League title 
Pedro’s early opener was cancelled out by a wonder free-kick from Burnley’s new £13million signing Robbie Brady By CHARLIE WYETT
